new-game-intro-body =
  Dreams.
  
  It started with the dreams.
  
  Dreams of hidden worlds -
  Dreams of endless skies -
  
  Dreams of terror.
  
  Dreams of darkness, mysteries, and power consumed my nights.
  I felt there was something real there, in those nocturnal visions.
  Something of the substance of the world.
  Something hitherto unknown to the waking lives of homo sapiens.
  
  I studied the science of sleep and dreaming, but didn't find what I needed to understand what was happening to me.
  
  I cast my net wider, reading the works of kooks and cranks, visionaries and madmen, anything to make sense of the dreams that disturbed my nights and days.
  
  I collected obscure books.
  I experimented on my own mind.
  I ingested strange substances.
  
  One day, I realized that I could not do this alone.
  I needed helpers. Assistants. Co-conspirators.
  I needed fellow explorers on this strange path into darkness and the deep realms.
new-game-confirm = A cult was born
